SUMMARY:Brunch In Bloom at Gary Farrell Vineyards
DESCRIPTION:Brunch In Bloom: Rosé &amp; Sauvignon Blanc Release at Gary Farrell Vineyards invites guests to be among the first to taste the 2025 Rosé of Pinot Noir and 2025 Sauvignon Blanc during a relaxed\, intimate brunch on the Overlook. Sip and swirl these new releases while mingling with fellow wine lovers and enjoying the sunshine.    The casual buffet features pastries\, quiche\, fresh spring salad\, seasonal fruit\, coffee\, and iced tea\, with vegetarian options available. Additional wines\, including Pinot Noir and Chardonnay\, will also be available for purchase\, making this a perfect springtime celebration of new releases and great company.
URL:https://www.sonoma.com/event/brunch-in-bloom-at-gary-farrell-vineyards/
LOCATION:10701 Westside Road, Healdsburg, CA, 95448, United States
GEO:-122.897356;38.5072959
CATEGORIES:Celebration,Dining,Drink,Food,Food & Wine,Sonoma County,Wine
