SUMMARY:Spring Celebration at Charlie's Acres
DESCRIPTION:Charlie’s Acres hosts a family-friendly Spring Celebration\, inviting guests to enjoy a fun and meaningful day surrounded by rescued animals. Visitors can explore the sanctuary on a guided loop\, meet the animal residents\, and learn their rescue stories while offering gentle treats and affection.    The event also features festive food available for purchase\, a kid-friendly scavenger hunt\, and indoor and outdoor games for all ages\, with chances to win prizes. Designed to be both entertaining and educational\, the celebration offers a heartwarming way to connect with animals and the community.    Held rain or shine\, proceeds from the event support the lifelong care of over 150 rescued animals and fund free humane education programs for schools.
URL:https://www.sonoma.com/event/spring-celebration-at-charlies-acres/
LOCATION:3201 Napa Road, Sonoma, CA, 95476, United States
CATEGORIES:Celebration,Family Friendly,Outdoors
