SUMMARY:Great Gatsby Party at The Lounge at Mercy
DESCRIPTION:Step into a world of 1920s glamour at the Roaring 420’s Gatsby Party\, an immersive evening where vintage elegance meets modern indulgence. Set inside The Lounge at Mercy\, the space transforms into a lavish speakeasy filled with golden details\, velvet vibes\, and jazz-era energy.    Enjoy a live performance by Fog City Swing\, delivering dance-worthy big band sounds\, along with a full dinner experience and curated goodie bag. Sip cannabis-infused cocktails\, explore interactive brand stations\, and take part in guided tastings designed to elevate the evening. Guests can also enjoy casino-style games and live entertainment throughout the night.    Dress to impress for the Gatsby Costume Contest—think flapper dresses and sharp suits\, for a chance to stand out. This 21+ event invites you to indulge\, socialize\, and celebrate in true roaring style.
URL:https://www.sonoma.com/event/great-gatsby-party-at-the-lounge-at-mercy/
LOCATION:7950 Redwood Dr, , Cotati, CA, 94931, United States
CATEGORIES:Dining,Drink,Food,Food & Wine,Performing Arts,Sonoma County,Wine
ATTACH;FMTTYPE=image/jpeg:https://winecountry-media.s3.amazonaws.com/wp-content/uploads/sites/5/2026/04/06232907/Roaring-420s-500-x-500-Sonoma-County-Tourism-scaled.jpg
