SUMMARY:Spring Hike &amp; Light Lunch at Sonoma Raceway
DESCRIPTION:Join the Sonoma Overlook Trail Stewards for a Spring Hike &amp; Light Lunch at Sonoma Raceway. Explore scenic trails across the Raceway’s 1\,600-acre property\, with your choice of a three- or five-mile hike featuring stunning bay views\, vineyards\, wildflowers\, and even “woolly weeders” at work.    The event begins at 10 AM (gates open at 9:30) and concludes by 3 PM\, followed by a light lunch. This popular annual fundraiser supports trail maintenance for the heavily visited Sonoma Overlook Trail\, helping keep it accessible and well maintained year-round. Trail stewards will be on hand to hike alongside guests\, making it a fun and meaningful way to give back while enjoying Sonoma’s natural beauty.
URL:https://www.sonoma.com/event/spring-hike-light-lunch-at-sonoma-raceway/
LOCATION:29355 Arnold Dr (Hwy 121), Sonoma, CA, 95476, United States
GEO:-122.4693688;38.2315738
CATEGORIES:Food,Outdoors,Sonoma County
ATTACH;FMTTYPE=image/png:https://winecountry-media.s3.amazonaws.com/wp-content/uploads/sites/5/2026/04/03211457/SpringHike1000px.png
END:VEVENT
