SUMMARY:Winemaker for a Day Lunch Experience at Lynmar Estate
DESCRIPTION:Have you ever wondered what it is like to be a winemaker? This is your invitation to step into the cellar with Lynmar Estate Winemaker Pete Soergel for an immersive journey into the art and science of crafting exceptional wine.    Your experience begins with an exclusive tour of their production facilities\, followed by a hands-on blending seminar. Taste and blend four distinct barrel samples to create your own unique cuvée alongside fellow members. Pete will evaluate the blends and select one as a potential candidate for the 2025 vintage.    After your time in the cellar\, gather for a thoughtfully prepared lunch paired with finished wines\, continuing the conversation about the magical transformation from grape to glass. As always\, the afternoon concludes in true Lynmar fashion with beautiful food\, extraordinary wine\, wonderful company\, and memories in the making.    Price includes guided tour\, wine\, food\, and community. Space is limited\, so reserve your spot today!
URL:https://www.sonoma.com/event/winemaker-for-a-day-lunch-experience-at-lynmar-estate/
LOCATION:3909 Frei Rd, Sebastopol, CA, 95472, United States
GEO:-122.8445728;38.4421027
CATEGORIES:Dining,Drink,Food,Food & Wine,Food and Wine Pairing,Sonoma County,Wine,Wine Education,Wine Tasting
ATTACH;FMTTYPE=image/jpeg:https://winecountry-media.s3.amazonaws.com/wp-content/uploads/sites/5/2026/04/05010856/Lynmar-Estate.jpg
END:VEVENT
